4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aspiring to become cybersecurity specialists without prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced knowledge in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp culminates in an official completion certificate recognized by multiple institutions. Courses can be conducted in either English or Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop